stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Pending
  Pending --> Implemented: Mark Implemented
  Pending --> Reviewed: Mark Reviewed
  Pending --> Declined: Decline

  Implemented --> [*]
  Reviewed --> [*]
  Declined --> [*]

  note right of Pending
    Pending items are action-eligible.
    Modal allows optional manager response.
  end note

  note right of Implemented
    Represents accommodation completed
    in menu or process.
  end note

  note right of Reviewed
    Represents assessment completed
    without full implementation.
  end note

  note right of Declined
    Represents unsupported request.
  end note
